  itemIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9e0d34f29facff84981eb257a7b5647f, type: 3}
  description: 'Increases Ability Power by 30 and Health by 30 and attack damage
    by 15%. Grants "Essence Transfer": The wearer heals for 20% of all damage dealt
    (both from abilities and basic attacks). Additionally, whenever the wearer heals
    themselves through this effect, 50% of that healing is also granted to the ally
    with the lowest current Health. A crystal vial filled with ethereally pulsing
    blood that resonates with every blow struck; it acts as a spiritual siphon, weaving
    the life force stolen from enemies into a mending wave for those most in need.'
